name: deep_codegen_mixed_arith_if_operand
section: codegen-arithmetic-dispatch
args: cond:Bool a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: PHI-selected Int values must compose through arithmetic.
law: (= (+ (if {cond} {a} {b}) (if {cond} {c} {d})) (if {cond} (+ {a} {c}) (+ {b} {d})))
